commit.message: Added a line about the examples
Added example images of image and bio algorithms
Updated text analysis algorithm, stop-word dictionary and custom dictionary to recognize and treat differently, keywords/phrases starting with 'no','not', etc.

Added psd file for logo

...because I was clearing my desktop
Added a new file 'automate.py' which solely demos the algorithm. The script 'test.py' can be used to test changes to the algorithm.
Added function to build word_list dictionary from a .txt file instead of hardcoding it.
Changed image analysis algorithm, how images are accessed in loop etc.
